text.tspan: You're waking up on the bed (1)
Lift up the pillow and get your smartphone (2)
Turn off the pnone and recover graphical password by glares
when you turn the phone to the light source (3)
Unlock the phone and you'll get the pass to open the toolbox (4)
In the toolbox you'll find many instruments, you need to grab the screwdriver
Pick up the alarm clock (5) and open backside panel to get the batteries
Open backside of the radio (6), eject discharged battery and insert the charged one
Walk in the room to get the point where you'll catch the radiovawe,
then listen to hear the code from the door pinpad (7)
